title: $:/plugins/crosseye/json-convert/readme

! JSON Convert

A general-purpose JSON-to-tiddler converter, with reusable mapping
profiles, a staging area for preview and collision resolution, and
tolerant input handling.

* Open the [[Console|$:/plugins/crosseye/json-convert/Console]] to
  paste source JSON, pick a profile, and run a conversion.
* Manage mapping profiles in the
  [[Editor|$:/plugins/crosseye/json-convert/Editor]] — launched from
  the Console's ''Edit'' / ''New…'' buttons.
* Mapping profiles are tiddlers tagged `$:/tags/json-convert/mapping`.
  Custom transforms are tiddlers tagged
  `$:/tags/json-convert/transform` (JavaScript bodies, `value` in
  scope).

